evidence.location: Throughout Docket, Complaint, and Order/Opinion documents
evidence.text: No other case numbers are referenced in any document. The Docket entries reference internal document numbers (e.g., 're 8', 're 23'), not related case codes. The Complaint and Order consistently reference only the main case number 'Case 3:25-cv-04870-CRB' without mentioning any other case numbers as related matters.
